  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_ratansi_arVol01Doc04.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>بمنّه تعالى</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>By the Grace of God</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#hilal">السيد هلال بن سعيد بن محمد بن سليمان البسعيدي</persName>
               بأن عليه
               <persName ref="#ratansi">لرطنسيه بن برشوتم البانياني</persName>
               ثلاثة ارباع قرش فضه
               <lb/>و ثلاثة قروش افرنسيسيات فضة واربعين قرشا فضة افرنسيسياً و مأتين قرش فضة افرنسيسي و قد باع له بحقه  
               <lb/>هذا ماله القطعة اللذي شرقي الساقية من الباده التاسعة من
               <placeName ref="#haylAlGhaf">حيل الغاف</placeName>
               بما بها النخل والفسل والشجر و ماله
               <lb/>من الحدود والطرق والسواقي مع مشربه المعتاد لسقيه من فلج
               <placeName ref="#haylAlGhaf">حیل الغاف</placeName>
               على دوب اواده بيع القطع وله الإقالة
               <lb/>في ذلك الى مضي تسعة اشهر زمانا من يومنا هذا باقراره له بذلك بتاريخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">يوم العشرين من شهر شوال
               <num>١٣٠٥</num></date>
               <lb/>و كتبه الفقير 
               <persName ref="#hamoud">حمود بن عبدالله بن محمد المنذري</persName>
               بيده
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>The <persName ref="#hilal">Sayyed Hilal bin Said bin Mohammed bin Sulaiman Al-Busaidi</persName> acknowledges that he owes <persName ref="#ratansi">Ratansi bin Purshottam Al-Banyani</persName> <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="243.75">three-quarters of a silver <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qirsh</ref>
               <lb/>and three silver French <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref>, and forty silver French <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref>, and two hundred French <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref></measure>, and that he has sold to him his rights to
               <lb/>this land that is east of the irrigation canal, including the ninth time-share in <placeName ref="#haylAlGhaf">Hayl Al-Ghaf</placeName>, and what it has in palms and saplings and trees and what appertains to it
               <lb/>in terms of boundaries and roads and irrigation canals, and its usual amount of irrigation from the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_falaj">falaj</ref> of <placeName ref="#haylAlGhaf">Hayl Al-Ghaf</placeName><gap/> [and this is] a complete sale, and he has the right to cancel
               <lb/>it for up to nine months’ time from this date, by his acknowledgment of it, this <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">twentieth day of Shawwal 1305</date>.
               <lb/>And it was written by the wretched <persName ref="#hamoud">Hamoud bin Abdullah bin Mohammed Al-Mandhiri</persName>, by his own hand.
            </p>
         </div>
